name: The aesthetics of panel houses | LoRA
description:
This LoRA allows you to create panel houses from the post-Soviet era, in the style of "Khrushchevka".

Trigger Words is not necessary, but it is better to add "russian panel houses".

P.S. If you want to support me, subscribe to my Telegram or Instagram

modelVersions.name: v1.05
modelVersions.description: A FP16 version with better detailing of houses. Works best with "The Ally's Mix III" model
